  <paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1536798488189">
   <div>
    Diese Geschichte handelt von einem Mädchen namens
   </div>
   <div>
    <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1536798170250" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">
